cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.CG, cs.DM, cs.IT. 

The paper deals with combinatorial optimization problems with a geometric structure, which suggests categories such as cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CG (Computational Geometry). The use of property testing also suggests categories such as cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the focus on LP-Type problems suggests cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics).
